title: Photos from the 89th Oscars Red Carpet
text:
SHARE Photos from the 89th Oscars red carpet 
Jimmy Kimmel hosts the 89th Annual Academy Awards on Sunday night, but before the show kicks off, the stars walked the red carpet. You can view the 89th Oscars red carpet photos in the gallery below! You can also check out the full list of Oscars nominations and winners as they are announced by clicking here . 
The 89th Academy Awards are being held on Sunday, February 26, 2017, at the Dolby Theatre at Hollywood & Highland Center in Hollywood, and televised live on the ABC Television Network at 7 p.m. ET/4 p.m. PT. The Oscars are also televised live in more than 225 countries and territories worldwide. 
If you missed them, you can still view red carpet photos from the 2017 Golden Globe Awards and from last yearâ€™s 88th Annual Academy Awards . Photos from other film premieres, such as Star Wars: The Force Awakens , can be viewed by clicking here . 
Who stood out to you in the 89th Oscars red carpet photos? Let us know in the comments below!
